Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这次开始在节目的最后会有
